    Unsupervised --> UnsupervisedTask{Task<br/>Type?}
    UnsupervisedTask -->|Clustering| Clustering[Clustering]
    UnsupervisedTask -->|Dimensionality Reduction| DimReduction[Dimensionality Reduction]

    Clustering --> ClusterAlgo{Algorithm?}
