    ClusterAlgo -->|DBSCAN| DBSCAN[DBSCAN<br/>scikit-learn]
    ClusterAlgo -->|Autoencoder| AE[Autoencoder<br/>TensorFlow/PyTorch]

    DimReduction --> DimAlgo{Algorithm?}
    DimAlgo -->|PCA| PCA[PCA<br/>SageMaker built-in]
    DimAlgo -->|t-SNE| TSNE[t-SNE<br/>scikit-learn]

    Reinforcement --> RLAlgo{Algorithm?}
    RLAlgo -->|PPO| PPO[PPO<br/>Ray RLlib]
    RLAlgo -->|DQN| DQN[DQN<br/>Ray RLlib]
    RLAlgo -->|A3C| A3C[A3C<br/>Ray RLlib]

